creator: Connie Bullock
descriptionHtml:
GranvilleOne is your source for information and news at Granville Health System. With push notifications, you are up to date - always and everywhere. On top of that, the app offers the following features:

• Announcements & Alerts
• Upcoming Events
• Job Postings
• Suggestions & Requests
• Social Media & Photo Galleries
• and much more!

Stay tuned!
descriptionShort: GranvilleOne is your source for information and news at Granville Health System

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• A new version of chat with a sleek user interface is now available.
• The global search function in the app has been improved to show the most relevant content faster.
• The new version of the Employee Directory allows you to filter users by department, location, and more.
• You can now tag users in comments using @mentions.
• The Change password function has been improved for enhanced security.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• There is a new way to create posts directly and more quickly using the Post widget.
• On-demand translation is now also available for all widgets.
• Editors can now create content in Afrikaans, Malagasy, Mongolian and Zulu.
• The latest newsfeed and News Stage widget are now available for all. This includes endless scrolling, liking and commenting from the newsfeed, and more!
• On pages, bullet points did not match the text color. This has been fixed.
